Welcome to my playthrough of Beautiful Desolation, a post-apocalyptic adventure game by Brotherhood Games, the same people behind Stasis. Join me as we travel a bizarre wasteland with our brother and a robotic dog companion POOCH looking for a way back to some semblance of normalcy.

Official site:
http://www.thebrotherhoodgames.com

You can buy the game on PC at:
https://www.gog.com/game/beautiful_desolation
https://store.steampowered.com/app/912570/BEAUTIFUL_DESOLATION/
